Subject: RE: [T2] Little piece under rear side window.

> There's a little piece of sheet metal that runs along the belt line under
> the rear driver's side window.  It has three screws underneath.  I have
> removed these, but it is still attached.  I can't see or feel any other
> fasteners.
>
> Can I remove this piece, and if so, how?



It pushes downward into a channel.  If you have removed the screws, try
tapping it upward using a rubber mallet; it should pop off.

